      <title>They said Apple would never make this</title>
      <description><![CDATA[<p>Last week, Apple unveiled 7 new product updates, including a brand new MacBook at a price point they've literally never done before. In today's episode, I discuss why things do change and how Apple punditry tends to assume whatever Apple currently does is everything they will ever do. Oh, I also have some opinions on all 7 products.</p>
<p>Video version here <a href="https://youtu.be/qsxE3jy6lDk" rel="noopener noreferrer">https://youtu.be/qsxE3jy6lDk</a></p>
<p><p>Most episodes are <a href="https://www.youtube.com/@ABetterComputer">available on YouTube</a> as well.</p></p>]]></description>
      <pubDate>Mon, 9 Mar 2026 09:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <author>matt@birchtree.me (Matt Birchler)</author>
      <link>https://a-better-computer.simplecast.com/episodes/they-said-apple-would-never-make-this-pH5p5eO8</link>
