      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Last week, Apple unveiled 7 new product updates, including a brand new MacBook at a price point they've literally never done before. In today's episode, I discuss why things do change and how Apple punditry tends to assume whatever Apple currently does is everything they will ever do. Oh, I also have some opinions on all 7 products.</p>
<p>Video version here <a href="https://youtu.be/qsxE3jy6lDk" rel="noopener noreferrer">https://youtu.be/qsxE3jy6lDk</a></p>
<p><p>Most episodes are <a href="https://www.youtube.com/@ABetterComputer">available on YouTube</a> as well.</p></p>]]></content:encoded>
